name: City of Toronto Vintage Map Pillow
description:
A genuine vintage-style linen pillow case with 100% down-filled insert.  The pillow case has a real, 1873 City of Toronto road map printed on it.  Cool original city details on the map make it fun to explore - 'New Gaol', Lunatic Asylum(s) and a river running through Queen's Park! 

Makes a great gift.

Details: This is a 100% linen-cotton canvas pillow, down filled, 12 by 18 inches.

<b>Price includes shipping inside Canada!<b>

name: Muskoka Lakes Vintage Map Pillow
description:
A genuine vintage-style linen pillow case with 100% down-filled insert.  The pillow case has a map of the Muskoka Lakes circa 1920 printed on it.  Spans Georgian Bay to the 3 main Muskoka Lakes,  Rosseau, Joseph and Muskoka, and east to Huntsville.

Makes a great hostess gift!

Details: This is a 100% linen-cotton canvas pillow, down filled, 12 by 18 inches.

<b>Price includes shipping inside Canada!<b>

name: Vintage Canada Stamp Pillow
description:
A genuine vintage-style linen pillow case with 100% down-filled insert.  The pillow case is printed with an image of the famous Canadian postage stamp: Xmas 1898 featuring the British Empire at the time highlighted in red. British North America, Australia & New Zealand, South Africa, Gibraltar, India, etc.

Makes a great gift for the stamp collector in your life!

Details: This is a 100% linen-cotton canvas pillow, down filled, 12 by 18 inches.
The backing fabric is a heavy black cotton/canvas.

<b>Price includes shipping inside Canada!<b>
